    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2011 BMW M3 Coupe, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen remains in exemplary condition, featuring documented preventative rod bearing replacement and a flawless subframe. The high-revving powerplant delivers a linear torque curve up to its 8,400 RPM redline, managed by the M Variable Differential Lock for peerless longitudinal traction. Equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the Competition Package (ZCP), the suspension geometry and damping rates remain factory-spec. Zero bolster wear on the Novillo leather and original paint meter readings across all panels confirm its concours-level preservation. A purist\u2019s example with zero mechanical compromises.",
      "price": 48500.0,
